##### Installing Ionic (Ubuntu)

1 :heavy_minus_sign: "$ sudo apt-get update"
2 :heavy_minus_sign: "$sudo apt-get upgrade"
3 :heavy_minus_sign: Visit page: http://ionicframework.com/getting-started/
4 :heavy_minus_sign: Follow instructions on the web page

#### Cloning Our Repo

1 :heavy_minus_sign: Go to our repo page at: https://github.com/ChicoState/CSUDeals
2 :heavy_minus_sign: On your terminal, run "$ git clone git@github.com:ChicoState/CSUDeals.git"

#### Running the App

1 :heavy_minus_sign: Go into the project folder: "$ cd ../CSUDeals/CSUDeals"
2 :heavy_minus_sign: "ionic serve"
